{
  "stem": "1338.6",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "I was blind with ambition that I wasn't going that war to let me down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "I was going to make something of myself.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "Kibbutz was very good to me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "I worked there.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "And when I-- when they knew that I was studying, I was studying for matriculation papers, because I didn't have a high school diploma.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So there was a service for the British colonial service.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "There was a British matriculation papers, the London matriculation papers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "You could get a high school degree by correspondence.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I studied.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I remember, I-- after 14 hours in the field or 10 hours in the field, I would study with the oil lamp in the tent and cry, and study.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "By the way, it worked out very well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I want to tell you something about that, too, if we have time.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Something, maybe a lesson about what does-- how you should study, and what does it mean to learn.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But anyway, I-- they wanted me, even after a while, it looked like the kibbutz would even consider, because they knew I was so obsessed with going to college that they decided maybe they'll send me to college.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And there was a rumor about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I could probably pursue it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But I just felt that I cannot make any commitment.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "This is a terrible moral commitment.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, there was no contract that you sign.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But if a kibbutz sends you, in those days-- you know, this is not today where everybody goes to college.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Very few people went to college.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The whole technical college in Haifa had 600 people, of which the entering class was 150.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So you-- you just did not go to college as a routine.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
